title: Ranking Every SAW Movie from Worst to Best (SAW - Jigsaw)
author: Reel Talk
comment: 6, especially the carousel trap is my favorite
I love saw 6. Rewatched it recently because my insurance company will no longer cover my old painkiller and I have to find a new one. It’s cathartic

1. Saw VI
2. Saw IV
3. Saw II

Jigsaw/Saw 8 would definitely be last place for me. Saw 7/3D would be second to last. I'd struggle to rank the first 6 in any order because I enjoy them all so much.
Saw 2.. And nothing even comes close to it. The twists and everything else with it was mind boggling..
